The paper deals with image steganalysis using deep learning, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the use of hand-crafted features and the integration of domain knowledge, which are common in the computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) categories. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV, followed by cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.LG, and cs.AI.
